<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٦٣-<span class="c5"> كَتَبَ إِلَيَّ يُوسُفُ بْنُ عَبْدِ اللَّهِ الْإِسْكَافِيُّ أَنَّ الْحَسَنَ بْنَ عَلِيِّ بْنِ الْحَسَنِ حَدَّثَهُمْ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗١٤٣⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>أَنَّ أَبَا عَبْدِ اللَّهِ سُئِلَ عَنِ التَّوْقِيتِ فِي حَلْقِ الْعَانَةِ وَنَتْفِ الْإِبِطِ؟<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ:</span> لَا يثبت.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>